This riflescope offers a 6.5x magnification coupled with a 50 mm objective lens that provides a detailed and vivid view, at a distance of up to 200 yards. Using its video output jack, you can attach an external recording device to it and capture your adventures for the day. It offers six digital reticle options in green, white and red, so you can use this riflescope for long-distance targets. For added convenience, it lets you adjust the windage and elevation levels.  I have the original box, case and manual for it. As I said this is barely used and when I checked it still works fine. The AR upper is made by DTI and is a 1/9 ratio. Has the BCG included. I included a pull loop that attaches to the charging handle. This makes it a ton easier to charge the rifle while this scope on it. Will also include the scope mounts by NC Star.
